                    <div class="info">
                        <p><span class="emoji">ðŸ‘†</span> TENTATIVAS: 3</p>
                        <p><span class="emoji">ðŸŽ²</span> CASA DE APOSTAS: Placard bet</p>
                        <p><span class="emoji">ðŸ’¥</span> BOMBAS: 3</p>
                        <p><span class="emoji">ðŸ•‘</span> VÃ¡lido atÃ©: <span id="valid-time"></span></p>
                    </div>
                    <div id="message"></div>
                    <div id="countdown"></div>
